	<section class="content-section">
		<h2>Signs You Might Need an Extraction</h2>
		<p>Not all wisdom teeth need to be removed, but you should see a dentist if you experience:</p>
		<ul>
			<li>Severe pain or stiffness in the jaw near the back of your mouth.</li>
			<li>Swollen, red, or bleeding gums.</li>
			<li>Difficulty opening your mouth or chewing.</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

