		<div class="faq">
			<details>
				<summary>Does getting a wisdom tooth pulled hurt?</summary>
				<p>We use local anesthesia to ensure you don't feel pain during the procedure. You will only feel some pressure. We also provide clear aftercare instructions to manage post-op discomfort.</p>
			</details>
			<details>
				<summary>Is tooth extraction covered by insurance or CDCP?</summary>
				<p>Most private insurances and the CDCP cover basic extractions. We will help you confirm your coverage before the procedure.</p>
			</details>
